OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FMainly fine
OL,6,Fduring the evening, but becoming
OL,7,Frather cloudy from the west, with a
OL,8,Flittle rain and drizzle spreading
OL,9,Feastwards throughout the night.
OL,10,FStaying warm and feeling muggy at
OL,11,Ftimes, with light winds.
OL,12,
OL,13,CWednesday:FBrightest in the southeast,
OL,14,Fwith some sunny spells here. Cloudier
OL,15,Fin the northwest and some southern
OL,16,Fcoastal districts, with periods of
OL,17,Fmostly light rain, easing later. Warm
OL,18,Fand rather humid.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
