OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,6,FMostly fine with some sunshine.
OL,7,FTurning increasingly hot and humid
OL,8,Ftowards the weekend. Staying mainly
OL,9,Fdry, but with the possibility of
OL,10,Fthunderstorms on Friday and Saturday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
